desc.en: Taizhou Rail Transit is a municipal railway system serving Taizhou City, Zhejiang Province, China. Its first line, Taizhou Rail Transit, was opened on December 28, 2022.
desc.zh-Hans: 台州轨道交通，是服务于中国浙江省台州市的市域铁路系统，其首条线路台州市域铁路S1线于2022年12月28日开通运营

updateHistory.reason: As of December 2022 Taizhou Rail Transit has opened one line of Taizhou Municipal Railway S1
